{"tid":920530,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"『業主實力』唔加息，8月價再mark 高20%","createTime":"2018-11-29T01:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T03:10:20.000Z","uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7c50da760b5a0f911c061baf4bfbabc5922f45e3","tid":920530,"uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:21:04.000Z","msg":"外電報道，美國聯儲局主席鮑威爾於論壇上表示，目前利率僅稍低於中性利率，市場解讀為聯儲局之利率正常化進程將進入尾聲。鮑威爾指，即使是最準確的預測，亦會面對不可預知的狀況，循序漸進的加息進程亦旨在平衡風險，亦有密切監控經濟數據。 他又指，注意到加息太快將收窄經濟增長的風險，加息太慢則會導致通脹及金融市場波動。 聯儲局亦發布首份金融穩定報告，憂慮中美貿易關係緊張、英國脫歐帶來的市場波動，及中國及新興市場之經濟問題將影響美國金融系統，或推動資產價格及影響信貸質素。報告亦指出，即使出現不能預計的經濟打擊，金融系統亦可保持穩定，惟企業之高槓桿借貸或在經濟下行時面對更大風險。(vi/t)\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n2018/11/29 09:10<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"159b6b000a67c380cff5f1b29d30a41f2ad96f5b","tid":920530,"uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:11:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284567a65b762fe2c47ce1b71f2325bdc0248812","tid":920530,"uid":68097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"聽講好多新盤售樓處一早就出現人龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f699bf5ba545ceec76dcb28ae023685f262f7d1","tid":920530,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"284567a65b762fe2c47ce1b71f2325bdc0248812","tid":920530,"uid":68097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:12:49.000Z","msg":"聽講好多新盤售樓處一早就出現人龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T02:21:51.000Z","msg":"鬼排既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72a69bf11795bb47791e89e5f8cc4773510e0c42","tid